{"tid":2151631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"訪問四日 今晤蔡英文  美衞生部長抵台 日媒：研設新WHO","createTime":"2020-08-11T13:11:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T13:33:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a304d16676d40ec4d9bd127cb54214bd12b670d1","tid":2151631,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:11:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200810/QIAEUMROQ4QALPZPG6JSVS5DWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200810%2FQIAEUMROQ4QALPZPG6JSVS5DWE%2F&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=bd632bba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200810%2FQIAEUMROQ4QALPZPG6JSVS5DWE%2F&h=36430fa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200810/QIAEUMROQ4QALPZPG6JSVS5DWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n訪問四日 今晤蔡英文 <br />\n美衞生部長抵台 日媒：研設新WHO<br />\n<br />\n【加強聯繫】<br />\n<br />\n中美關係急劇惡化之際，美國派遣1979年與台灣斷交以來最高級別的官員訪台。衞生與公共服務部長阿扎爾（Alex Azar）昨率團乘搭尾翼漆有美國國旗的行政專機抵台進行四日訪問，是為六年來再有內閣成員訪台。阿扎爾今日將與總統蔡英文會晤，有消息指雙方將就設立取代世界衞生組織的新國際組織交換意見。他還將簽署美台公共衞生合作備忘錄，最後一天將弔唁早前病逝的前總統李登輝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-kfy8hNgazhYdEFXukue1D-Nzd8=/636x357/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WGB7KPR7XJAHKPBYXIVNWQCTQA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-kfy8hNgazhYdEFXukue1D-Nzd8%3D%2F636x357%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWGB7KPR7XJAHKPBYXIVNWQCTQA.gif&h=a265b6cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡英文今將與美國衞生部長阿扎爾會晤。<br />\n<br />\n台灣行政院早前稱，阿扎爾這次是代。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n日本《產經新聞》引述台灣政府消息稱，阿。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Jfb4uxIAMsQd0ulo82ncnobazGs=/202x357/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DZA6VYV7BMPUUZX6DTUFRHKDRM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJfb4uxIAMsQd0ulo82ncnobazGs%3D%2F202x357%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDZA6VYV7BMPUUZX6DTUFRHKDRM.gif&h=4d26e20d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國衞生部長阿扎爾下機後，向傳媒揮手致意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乘坐「高規格」行政專機<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：日前首相森喜朗率團弔唁李登輝<br />\n<br />\n阿扎爾。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n長期支持國民黨前主席洪秀柱的「。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DHeT3wnOjzTyiz9DTgxM71HuPe8=/190x104/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NBUFX7FHHWRMPWBALDDNYYAASU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDHeT3wnOjzTyiz9DTgxM71HuPe8%3D%2F190x104%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNBUFX7FHHWRMPWBALDDNYYAASU.gif&h=f13b452a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n代表團成員下機後，即進入機場「松風廳」貴賓室。台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fwv7HKn6y08ZGkP0kMh3-b1mJCo=/850x467/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XK4PA2XCLMKFU5H2AW6B2GV53E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ffwv7HKn6y08ZGkP0kMh3-b1mJCo%3D%2F850x467%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXK4PA2XCLMKFU5H2AW6B2GV53E.gif&h=3d9bdcdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿扎爾等人乘坐的行政專機，隸屬美國空軍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BI0ElsJE_Vv3kkm0nwSZrwSy5kQ=/567x369/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HVLY3CESO5VKDUBGGUVJ7ALF7Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBI0ElsJE_Vv3kkm0nwSZrwSy5kQ%3D%2F567x369%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHVLY3CESO5VKDUBGGUVJ7ALF7Q.gif&h=d8ea67b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美沒派國安官員避踩京「紅線」<br />\n<br />\n上一次美國內閣成員訪台是在2014年，。。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網/美聯社"},{"pid":"9d1a7d9c37d1bd9bd8f76d5cb1ad6481edfb6dd6","tid":2151631,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:12:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"957403c10668f3c2cf533d4ec81dab17db7801d8","tid":2151631,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:14:01.000Z","msg":"呢單新聞少咗好多人理"},{"pid":"1fe67f77fed5db9c47b4dd81d7c24302738e7f6a","tid":2151631,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc75300fa0d009816f6aacd227a597ea532a746","tid":2151631,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:15:55.000Z","msg":"國際聯盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87405ae0605dd7c1bcf384e24b594ad16989cc38","tid":2151631,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:16:54.000Z","msg":"WHO (-China/Russia)"},{"pid":"031509dade7fc2260eca58d28e7842dbefc73619","tid":2151631,"uid":126797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aec8c400ae8d835bc813e0dd15c64b238c07ddb","tid":2151631,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87405ae0605dd7c1bcf384e24b594ad16989cc38","tid":2151631,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:16:54.000Z","msg":"WHO (-China/Russia)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:33:23.000Z","msg":"加返俄仔好d<br />\n我地大中國可以以一對百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" 